question:
Problem A-2
Determine all solutions in real numbers \( x, y, z, w \) of the system
\[
\begin{aligned}
x+y+z & =w \\
\frac{1}{x}+\frac{1}{y}+\frac{1}{z} & =\frac{1}{w}
\end{aligned}
\]

